<td>Open sections with "[Entity] is a [category] that [differentiator]"</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>FAQ schema markup</td>
<td>Give answer engines machine-readable Q&amp;A pairs</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Concise answer blocks</td>
<td>Provide 40-60 word answers immediately after question headings</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>People Also Ask targeting</td>
<td>Structure content around the exact questions Google shows</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Voice search optimization</td>
<td>Use natural language, question-based headings</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>For targeting People Also Ask boxes specifically, read our <a href="/blog/optimize-people-also-ask/">PAA optimization guide</a>.</p>
<h3>What AEO Delivers</h3>
<p>AEO delivers brand visibility at the point of answer. Your business name, data, or expertise appears in <a href="/glossary/featured-snippet/">featured snippets</a>, AI Overviews, and voice responses.</p>
<p>The trade-off: you may not get a click. But you build brand awareness, topical authority, and trust with users who see your name as the source of the answer.</p>
<p>12% of Google queries show a featured snippet result. When your content wins that snippet, your brand appears above every organic listing on the page.</p>
