<p>For a complete GEO implementation guide, read our <a href="/blog/generative-engine-optimization-guide/">generative engine optimization guide</a>.</p>
<h3>What GEO Delivers</h3>
<p>GEO delivers brand citations inside AI responses. When ChatGPT mentions your business name, links to your content, or references your data, you reach users who never opened a search engine.</p>
<p>AI-generated traffic to U.S. retail sites increased 4,700% year-over-year as of July 2025. Fewer than 10% of sources cited by ChatGPT, Gemini, and Copilot rank in Google's top 10 for the same query. That means GEO is not just about SEO rankings. It is a separate visibility channel.</p>
